::Zeus/Ares/Killer::

Zeus fires missiles at the predacon base, ducking under autogun fire, as 
Annihilator's distress call reaches him. He looks at Shuko.

"Sir, I'll go help Annihilator!" he says, flying off toward the Newcomer's 
ship.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ares keeps firing at the Predacon base with all his guns.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killer yells, being hit by an autogun.

"I'm off to help Annihilator, Shuko!" he yells, turning to follow Zeus.
